Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.35,0:00:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.02,0:00:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.56,0:00:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.67,0:00:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.88,0:00:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.68,0:00:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.96,0:01:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.40,0:01:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.71,0:01:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.15,0:01:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親大人!請你快逃走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.92,0:01:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾，我在逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.06,0:01:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不是在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.53,0:01:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥沒有終結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我在逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.00,0:01:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果因此要我死，那也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.00,0:01:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用為了留戀宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.00,0:01:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連自己的生活方式改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.35,0:01:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.33,0:02:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十二話\N[爭取獨立之戰]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.81,0:02:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.01,0:02:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親善大使是個怎樣的人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.11,0:02:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部機動戰士是在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.98,0:02:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和Oz敵對的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們要先檢查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於宇宙衛星和Oz合併
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的形勢對地球影響很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.64,0:02:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我以一個國家的代表身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前來這裡打聽那方面的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個國家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.38,0:03:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.02,0:03:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是山克王國的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.99,0:03:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從大人自小就有交情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國前來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.56,0:03:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有聽聞\N在今次戰亂中開始復興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道戰爭會帶來甚麼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.80,0:03:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能向想擁有武力的衛星薦言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.37,0:03:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋求和平有很多方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能朝著更好的方向前進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.85,0:03:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳可以讓我\N在宇宙自由行動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳或許正在走\N一條的明智的路呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙不是Oz的叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯‧馬吉斯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙衛星D120
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是以前地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙司令部的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz現在沒有進行武力鎮壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.61,0:04:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並勸他們加入衛星議會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D120方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放棄了地球軍事組織的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直站在代表地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於宇宙的意向的立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舊聯合宇宙軍司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賽普提姆將軍的兒子金達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個衛星的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他身邊的舊聯合的人認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz從後推動的衛星獨立政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個嚴重問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在猶豫甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，Oz想擁有更強大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不戰鬥不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.21,0:04:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的科技\N對地球只會造成威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz只是把宇宙當作軍事工廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在能消滅他們的只有我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥會產生許多犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我們現在的兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.03,0:04:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也能考慮和他們談判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.46,0:04:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想把宇宙用來\N開發MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人兵器會令Oz做出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:05:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極其簡單的獨裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位全部有同一想法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.04,0:05:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯‧馬吉斯來了宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害怕宇宙武裝起來的是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以抽時間聽聽熟識Oz
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.95,0:05:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望地球和平的他的意見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開Oz的傑克斯.馬吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何來到這個宇宙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是個熱愛祖國的男子漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他知道無人行動就會出現危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.50,0:05:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是有意義的行動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那達\N你果然厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙正逐漸認同Oz
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校的表現很出色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.88,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她陸續和衛星建立起友好關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.82,0:05:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙建立國家的獨立心態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會生出生產性和防衛意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.93,0:06:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後以軍事國家的身份站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的各國感到威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.10,0:06:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會爭先恐後尋求Oz的支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起，特列斯，想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把宇宙變為羅姆斐拉的一份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲巴洛夫，準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了強化宇宙的軍備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲巴洛夫會前去生產MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.12,0:06:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校也爽快地同意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安她…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來非常喜歡MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.16,0:06:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人，久違了，我是蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和茲巴洛夫技師\N一起前來的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那件事，蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳打算怎樣處置MD?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把它們用作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會令大人你痛心的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的士兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.95,0:07:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人你真狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.09,0:07:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人你一定要站在世界的最高處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.03,0:07:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你把這世界棄於混亂中不顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.90,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為了協助大人你上來宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且為大人準備未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥不會從這世上消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.07,0:07:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，強者永遠統治世界就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.21,0:07:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們被強者支配覺得高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.95,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世上繼續戰鬥是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣會白流太多的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人你愛著所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有能成為神的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.53,0:07:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能從宇宙為地球建立和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.36,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂\N妳正以自己的理想看未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是大人你所希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.87,0:07:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的理想只是一個人類的妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.21,0:07:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歷史由日子累積而成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它對個人的未來無興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人你的未來已經早有定論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.05,0:08:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙才有大人你的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂，我並非那麼堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯和鋼彈的駕駛員們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在創造未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不須要回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時代會重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.50,0:08:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂，變回以前那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變回我以前好喜歡的蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.55,0:08:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有錯，是傑克斯‧馬吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.85,0:08:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯在宇宙出現了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.95,0:08:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他企圖和舊聯合的\N軍事衛星接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼哥爾特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅舊聯合宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然已經完成MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不用讓他們生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.06,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要給蕾蒂‧安特校\N今後的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.87,0:08:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴她我想要她的確認報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.28,0:09:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨，雖然我們曾是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.48,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但戰爭時代又令我們見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.65,0:09:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和關懷地球的聯合\N有同一立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽聞你為了宇宙衛星武裝一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從地球前來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是誕生新的軍事國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不覺得問題那麼嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果他們被Oz瞞騙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就不可以袖手旁觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.60,0:09:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz想把宇宙用作軍事工場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.48,0:09:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，地球的紛爭會加劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那會產生許多犧牲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.45,0:09:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的人有何看法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死去的領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.79,0:09:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯的思想並末過時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.79,0:09:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙不需要武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.06,0:09:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它作為沒被地球歷史\N污染的空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾經繁榮昌盛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為那是成為地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平主義國家榜樣的文化之源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為榜樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.54,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若宇宙的人再早一點\N聽到你的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.64,0:10:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們或許會打消念頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你告訴匹斯克拉福特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.64,0:10:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有我們為何一直在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.28,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在宇宙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.98,0:10:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，聯合被Oz推倒時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.19,0:10:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們曾經打算馬上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.13,0:10:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那會對宇宙留下很大的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙衛星是靠精密計算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,造成的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個管理中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必須維持著生活條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.77,0:10:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,檢查衛星的迴轉運動\N和大氣狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理天氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是以人手製造在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.31,0:10:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常自然出現\N的現象的人工物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裡環境生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.82,0:10:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,須要人類意識上的改革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.79,0:11:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不安，對，如果不能忘記不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.00,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不能在這裡活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.57,0:11:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不安的人會拿起武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武器能消除不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.47,0:11:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去到哪個地步不安會被消除?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙進攻地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋求穩定的大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Oz機動戰士的運輸艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們終於來攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一起迎擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.82,0:11:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的親善大使不可以戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會靈活運和兩副面孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.77,0:11:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在戰鬥中學會那種把戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.42,0:12:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是羅姆斐拉財團在宇宙製造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.45,0:12:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的地球降下計劃圖表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一次解決\N地球紛爭的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人都那樣認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.80,0:12:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒打算把MD派落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若遵照羅姆斐拉的主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.27,0:12:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球上只會流很多血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有力量的人統治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.75,0:12:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們以為只是那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球就會和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.92,0:12:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但大人否絕了統治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.79,0:12:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人一日不來宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世上就不會出現正確的秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.29,0:12:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的工作也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.77,0:12:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校妳還有身為Oz士兵的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為Oz士兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那結果會支持著大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.81,0:12:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士兵對任務忠實就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.78,0:13:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校妳已經成為\N超越士兵的領袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，特校妳優秀的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要以士兵的身份被發揮出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非作為引導大人的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是請妳作為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支持大人的Oz士兵效力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.96,0:13:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為支持特列斯大人的士兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.90,0:13:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人也應該希望那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.87,0:13:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人希望那樣…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.68,0:13:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在聯合軍基地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD開始交戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,600秒進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴爾吉雷射砲有效範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷射砲能給予\N聯合衛星多大損毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能破壞動力部份和管理設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一砲就能停止它的機能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽聞那個衛星除了軍人外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有很多平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是文職人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們清楚知道據守要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會成為攻擊目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事蕾蒂‧安特校知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是迪爾麥優公爵的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他們和背叛Oz的傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去準備麥丘留士和拜葉特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!特洛瓦‧巴頓!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我禁止你接近機動戰士閘門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.98,0:14:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論敵我，我不會相信叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校\N也不知道這件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校為了和聯合戰鬥出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.23,0:14:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切交由我指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,押下這傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為Oz的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會做出越權的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.51,0:14:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我對於特校的掩護部隊裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不採用拜葉特\N和麥丘留士的戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.88,0:14:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存有少許疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士兵不須要多加思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想和平的事給高層就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.99,0:14:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們追求的只是勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.62,0:15:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠近點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.85,0:15:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用近身戰彌補反應速度的差距
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.46,0:15:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.06,0:15:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里歐部隊損失50%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人陶拉斯全是MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.70,0:15:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是終防線20%被毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的平民避難完畢了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，已經用大型穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃到安全空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.95,0:15:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但區區MD不能攻陷這衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.68,0:15:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz的巴爾吉會作出最後一擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.12,0:15:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星要毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼意思?爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造衛星以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.99,0:15:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰爭裡被毀是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那有多悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.40,0:16:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人類有須要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把軍事力量帶來宇宙的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及想擁有軍事力量的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.24,0:16:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要在眼裡烙下錯誤的烙印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然也補償不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.55,0:16:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們的血能有用就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把爺爺你捲入這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.42,0:16:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那應該由我來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，金達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴爾吉能源砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.55,0:16:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們真的想擊毀衛星嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.39,0:17:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人希望戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能創造\N特列斯大人的未來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩下戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥是唯一的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.41,0:17:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不戰鬥就不能誕生任何東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯‧馬吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.95,0:17:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我永遠的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.36,0:17:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽聞你在宇宙出現，我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz正在改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的力量不足夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類要走的路太任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到擴張的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.61,0:17:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會把人類的心遺棄到這地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為Oz的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非是進行戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是培養有戰鬥心的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.58,0:18:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但戰鬥已經連人類也不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我作為一個士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.66,0:18:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑自己的意志選擇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗那潮流的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我沒有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改變羅姆斐拉選擇了的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.77,0:18:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能向了解我的知心好友傾訴\N我覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.60,0:18:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞，有另一個了解我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.94,0:18:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是關懷我\N擁有兩顆心的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近感到不安的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.55,0:18:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒資格談論未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.82,0:18:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜扥你，米利亞，替我救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要為了實現理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.07,0:18:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了特列斯大人而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合衛星進入射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能源炮發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是!蕾蒂‧安特校還在戰場!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊!兵士只要服從命令就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校會明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.57,0:19:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個蕾蒂‧安應該會阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對衛星的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.48,0:19:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她正在學習衛星的脆弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒打中?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避過了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶我去巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.31,0:20:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼哥爾，我以士兵的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.28,0:20:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上了很好的一課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是上課的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.45,0:20:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我身為指揮官不可以放過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.19,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行動是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.13,0:20:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我這行動也是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.51,0:20:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，我才沒有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為在這場混亂的戰鬥裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只能走士兵之路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.18,0:20:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團決定在月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.52,0:20:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造MD的生產工場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.25,0:20:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在月球量產的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是用來對付地球的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.96,0:20:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了馬上解決\N地球上的許多紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.26,0:20:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想出從宇宙直接降下部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.56,0:21:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把敵人殲滅的戰略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.70,0:21:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到最強武器的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.17,0:21:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝著不須要士兵\N力量的時代前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不明物體急速接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.44,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.98,0:21:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鋼彈，我們被鋼彈發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.78,0:21:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死MD的技師長嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我來說是瑣碎的目標啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.45,0:21:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地捕捉鋼彈的部隊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.69,0:21:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無子彈，無燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.23,0:21:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且沒剩下正常的推進機能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.46,0:21:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技師長\N我的性命就交由你保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.01,0:21:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,急速掉頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.41,0:21:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.17,0:21:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.48,0:21:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部鋼彈沒有反擊的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對那部機體有興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.98,0:21:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想盡可能在月面基地檢查它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.89,0:21:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地有聯絡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止攻擊並捉住鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.49,0:22:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你，仁慈的技師長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.87,0:22:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪吒，我們一定要強大起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.94,0:22:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有個工場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在那裡幫我們增強嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.74,0:22:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.69,0:22:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.69,0:22:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.69,0:22:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.69,0:22:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.19,0:22:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.69,0:23:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.19,0:23:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.69,0:23:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.69,0:23:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.51,0:23:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.49,0:23:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護衛星，宇宙拿起武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.86,0:23:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然這是害怕地球來襲才決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但Oz在背後暗中活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.86,0:23:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了阻止量產機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.06,0:23:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐前去破壞月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.66,0:23:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在和衛星的志願兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.17,0:23:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希爾德的戰鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.83,0:23:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐看見迷途的衛星的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.41,0:23:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第二十三話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.64,0:23:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變回死神的迪歐

